dataset/44k/unicorn/unicorn_jp_001.wav|JA|ユニコーン級航空母艦・ユニコーン （HMS Unicorn）
dataset/44k/unicorn/unicorn_jp_002.wav|JA|ロイヤルネイビー…支援空母…ユニコーン…もともとはイラストリアス姉ちゃんを支援するために生まれた…あとはほかの姉ちゃんたちとともに行動したけど…みんなわたしに良くしてくれた。ユニコーンはね、いろんなところで頑張ったよ？…少しは頼りになるといいな……えへへ、もっと頑張るね？お兄ちゃんI'm... the support aircraft carrier of the royal navy... Unicorn. I was originally born to support big sister illustrious, but later on I mobilized with the other big sisters too. Everyone looked after me well. You know, Unicorn is giving her all in many ways. It would be nice if others will come to rely on me a little.... Ehehe, I'll work even harder, big brother.
